{"tid":1777794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東錦賽】裂頭腳直踢日本球員 國足負1:2輸波輸品","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T01:43:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"562606e7c546a8ca9b77d7007c90a4a84114ccc4","tid":1777794,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575980418_59db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575980418_59db.jpg&h=7932a9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191210/large/1575979284_dea3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191210%2Flarge%2F1575979284_dea3.jpg&h=bdded4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【中國1:2日本】<br />\n上半場30分鐘，球場上演了驚嚇的一幕，當時中國球員姜至鵬在中前場因踢人犯規，但這名國足後衞居然飛踢到日本後衞橋岡大樹的頭上，最終裁判只向姜至鵬出示黃牌。但在換邊後的70分鐘，日本透過一次角球攻勢，由三浦弦太頂入，幫助日本隊拉開比數；國足在90分鐘的唯一一次射門中框，便成功追回一球，董學升接應傳球頭槌頂入，最終日本隊仍然成功以2:1擊敗中國。<br />\n【中國0:1日本】<br />\n上半場完！暫時中國落後日本0:1。開賽初段，中國隊明顯比日本隊更積極。但是後者逐漸站穩陣腳，更在29分鐘取得入球，當時日本隊在左路打出配合，前鋒上田綺世後腳妙傳森島司入禁區傳中，鈴木武藏在姜至鵬身前將球撞入，這個入球是鈴木武藏在日本國家隊的處子入球。<br />\n17:56更新<br />\n國足正選陣容<br />\n門將：劉殿座<br />\n後衞：明天、李昂、梅方、姜至鵬<br />\n中場：馮勁、王上源、金敬道、張稀哲<br />\n前鋒：譚龍、董學升<br />\n日本正選陣容<br />\n門將：中村航輔<br />\n後衞：橋岡大樹、三浦弦太、畠中槙之輔、佐佐木翔<br />\n中場：井手口陽介、橋本拳人、森島司、遠藤溪太<br />\n前鋒：鈴木武藏、上田綺世<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191210/HBGXGU7HZVMVSGFV3UJPGDAVDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191210%2FHBGXGU7HZVMVSGFV3UJPGDAVDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=67024e74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191210%2FHBGXGU7HZVMVSGFV3UJPGDAVDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f0328223\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191210/HBGXGU7HZVMVSGFV3UJPGDAVDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"1181fff2639490b468c24aa4922dccd9d3f893ce","tid":1777794,"uid":70745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"少林足球？癡撚線"},{"pid":"06431d9f0b64d6c1b6340f79afb94132bd6981fc","tid":1777794,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩正想po"},{"pid":"5f2fd3fe1fe91492a9e9719bb4fa78840eb345d0","tid":1777794,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"班北京猿人幾十萬年都未進化過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310d55d9d5c330232980feae52bb31b9eae0da84","tid":1777794,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"支那隊對港隊個陣應該都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名睇支那輸波一地玻璃碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8a4f82fd7385efc1e8e77dac39244a1e039211","tid":1777794,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"最終裁判只向姜至鵬出示黃牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55cc22a3f7b07f3acfcfbccbd4baba0f42abec3","tid":1777794,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"6f9ac431cd4c0fea16cb2